---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
const title = "Mondly Review 2026: Is It Better Than Duolingo? | LearnEnglish.Life";
const description = "Our honest review of Mondly. Is it the best app for learning English vocabulary? We break down the features, pricing, and pros and cons.";
---
<Base title={title} description={description}>
  <Header />
  <main id="main-content" class="bg-neutral-950 min-h-screen">
<article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <div class="mb-8">
    <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Review · Updated April 2026</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">Mondly Review: Is It Better Than Duolingo?</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400">Mondly has made a name for itself with its gamified approach and innovative use of AR and VR. But for English learners, does it provide real results?</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-500">7.8</div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-bold text-white">Our Score</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-neutral-500">A solid choice for vocabulary</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-neutral-300">Mondly is excellent for beginners who want to build a foundation of words and phrases quickly. However, its lack of deep grammar explanations and limited speaking practice makes it less ideal for advanced learners.</p>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">What is Mondly?</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6">Mondly is a language learning app that focuses on conversational phrases and vocabulary. Unlike Duolingo, which uses a strict path, Mondly allows you to choose your own topics and learn at your own pace. It also offers unique features like Mondly VR and AR, which simulate real-life conversations.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">The Pros and Cons</h2>
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
    <div class="bg-emerald-900/20 border border-emerald-900/30 rounded-xl p-6">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-emerald-400 mb-4">Pros</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-300">
        <li>✅ Engaging gamified experience</li>
        <li>✅ Daily lessons keep you motivated</li>
        <li>✅ High-quality audio from native speakers</li>
        <li>✅ Innovative AR/VR features</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-red-900/20 border border-red-900/30 rounded-xl p-6">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-red-400 mb-4">Cons</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-300">
        <li>❌ Limited grammar explanations</li>
        <li>❌ Repetitive exercises</li>
        <li>❌ Not enough speaking practice</li>
        <li>❌ Most features require a subscription</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">Pricing</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6">Mondly offers a free version with one daily lesson. For full access, you'll need Mondly Premium, which costs around $9.99 per month or $47.99 per year. They often run promotions for lifetime access.</p>

  <div class="bg-emerald-600 rounded-xl p-8 text-center mt-12">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to try Mondly?</h3>
    <p class="text-emerald-100 mb-6">Start building your English vocabulary today.</p>
    <a href="https://www.mondly.com/" class="inline-block bg-white text-emerald-600 font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-100 transition">Visit Mondly</a>
  </div>
</article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
